welcome.subtitle: Intake24 is used in research, surveys and clinical studies to collect information about what people eat and drink.

participant.subtitle: You have landed on the main page for Intake24.
participant.link: To access Intake24 you will need your own survey link.
participant.info:
If you have been invited to take part in an Intake24 survey you should have been provided with a link.

Please check your invitation to take part. If you are unsure, please contact your research study team.
